nodes.text: Kara Reenogga was one of the Reenogga triplets and co-owner of Reenogga Personal Services, Cubed. She was known for her fiery temperament and stubbornness. She frequented Chabak's and enjoyed gambling, drinking contests, fistfights, and took pleasure in helping her friend Quink keep his cousin out of trouble by beating up anybody that was out to harm him.
